ðŸ§© How Providers Work

Think of it this way:

âž– Terraform = the builder
âž– Provider = the instruction manual
âž– Resource = the thing being built

The provider teaches Terraform the rules, APIs, and capabilities of a platform.

ðŸ›  Provider Syntax (AWS Example)

