 required_providers {
 aws = {
 source = "hashicorp/aws"
 version = "~> 5.0"
 }
 }
}

provider "aws" {
 region = "us-east-1"
}

âœ” required_providers â†’ tells Terraform which provider to download
âœ” provider "aws" â†’ configures how Terraform should talk to AWS

ðŸš€ Why Providers Matter:

1. Enable Terraform to work with hundreds of services
2. Standardize how infrastructure is created
3. Allow multi-cloud deployments with one tool
4. Make infrastructure portable, repeatable, and automated
5. Provide access to thousands of resource types

ðŸ§  Todayâ€™s Key Takeaway:

